{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"353499687f","title":"关于大批制问题的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"6b5251549f","index":0,"year":1967,"month":5,"day":2,"articleId":"353499687f"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wansui5","name":"毛泽东思想万岁(1961-1968卷)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui5a.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wansui5":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"47aaf62390","type":"title","text":"关于大批制问题的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"353499687f"},{"id":"6c0ce2ae78","type":"paragraph","text":"批判文章不要像九评那样长，每篇一、二千字，不要超过三千字。一篇一个中心，一个概念，明明白白。长了就没有人看，记不住。","index":1,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"353499687f"},{"id":"3c8742a07e","type":"paragraph","text":"同意。团结和服从都是有条件的，不是无条件的。","index":2,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"353499687f"},{"id":"0333f1208d","type":"paragraph","text":"年纪大的、年纪中的、年纪小的也要“三结合”，不要看不起年轻人。二十几岁、三十几岁的人都能做工作。搞“三结合”，要老中小，老的都会去见上帝的。","index":3,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"353499687f"},{"id":"1c1057f9d4","type":"paragraph","text":"今年形势好，布粮还是要抓。社论要搞快一些。批判文章文字要短。彭、罗、陆杨可以提为反革命修正主义，其他人都称修正主义分子。中国的赫鲁晓夫在文章中提，在标题上要提。","index":4,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"353499687f"},{"id":"1ff6892484","type":"paragraph","text":"×××","index":5,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"353499687f"},{"id":"b4222a9b45","type":"paragraph","text":"大批判要慎重，要确实，要调查清楚。调查清楚，批判才有力量，否则就会一风吹。引他（指刘少奇）的话不能只顾头不顾尾。批判要站得住。“托拉斯”这个名词，不能一概驳，主要驳他走资本主义道路。有些旧名词要赋予新的意义。","index":6,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"353499687f"},{"id":"6efd53492e","type":"paragraph","text":"“驯服工具论”要批判，但也要有无产阶级纪律。服从、团结，那是有条件的。","index":7,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"353499687f"},{"id":"09f60c9bec","type":"paragraph","text":"今年形势好，布、粮还是要抓。社论要搞快一些。","index":8,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"353499687f"},{"id":"8381310f82","type":"paragraph","text":"彭、罗、陆、杨可以称为“反革命修正主义分子”，其他人称“修正主义分子”。“中国的赫鲁晓夫，”文章中提，在标题上不要提。","index":9,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"353499687f"},{"id":"ebc708d6ef","type":"paragraph","text":"×××","index":10,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"353499687f"},{"id":"7956e9c4cc","type":"paragraph","text":"写文章要琢磨，要准确，要尖锐明确。","index":11,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"353499687f"},{"id":"8d72714443","type":"paragraph","text":"（1967 年 9 月）","index":12,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"353499687f"}],"page":{"id":"3046492838","publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"353499687f","start":589,"end":590}}}},"__N_SSG":true}